WEBVTT

00:08:29.047 --> 00:08:31.262
and he told us,

00:08:31.262 --> 00:08:35.421
"Syrians are just looking for a quiet place

00:08:35.421 --> 00:08:38.290
where nobody hurts you,

00:08:38.290 --> 00:08:40.832
where nobody humiliates you,

00:08:40.832 --> 00:08:43.543
and where nobody kills you."

00:08:43.543 --> 00:08:46.761
Well, I think that should be the minimum.

00:08:46.761 --> 00:08:49.888
How about a place of healing,

00:08:49.888 --> 00:08:51.766
of learning,

00:08:51.766 --> 00:08:55.160
and even opportunity?

00:08:56.832 --> 00:08:58.856
Americans and Europeans

00:08:58.856 --> 00:09:02.107
have the impression that proportionally